{"tid":1420004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】美列華為匯率操縱國 內地網民：神仙打架，百姓遭殃","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:34:09.000Z","uid":200550,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a21afc753645cca3ee0a65d3397a440ea6da48","tid":1420004,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:21:33.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰進一步升溫，繼中國相關企業暫停採購美國農產品後，美國財長姆欽（Steven Mnuchin）周一突然發表聲明，將中國列為匯率操縱國，是1994年來首次。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【股滙市況●不斷更新】美列華滙率操縱國 港股跌500點 專家：反彈值博率低<br />\n<br />\n兩國「短兵相接」，內地網民就「中國被指為匯率操縱國」議論紛紛。<span style=\"color: red;\">不少人繼續要無懼貿易戰，直言要中國政府打出「稀土牌」或「美債牌」</span>，不過有網民認為「貿易戰升級至金融戰」、「受苦都是老百姓」、「神仙打架，百姓遭殃」。<br />\n<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【開市前部署】不是貿易戰 是貨幣戰（股榮）<br />\n<br />\n流淡定：稀土牌，美債牌還出不出？人家快報雙了<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n歌者2向箔：開始掀桌子了！<br />\n<br />\n理金倉：貿易戰升級到金融戰<br />\n<br />\nycyy6473：叫口號有甚麼用，最後埋單和承受苦難的還是大眾百姓！<br />\n<br />\n選一個名字：的確是一場長期戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n周小林on：冬天來了<br />\n<br />\n看透人性才能擁有一切：現在真的可以說是內憂外患吶，希望這屆能挺過去<br />\n<br />\n風中的廠長：變成匯率操縱國標誌着毛衣戰（貿易戰）升級，繼續做好最壞打算吧<br />\n<br />\n一點趨勢：神仙打架，百姓遭殃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190806/59901971?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F59901971%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=c7bca37c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F59901971%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=4f8a9899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190806/59901971?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"5dc040278d82ede79b3a6ee5572a945ac9bb21fe","tid":1420004,"uid":200550,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:02.000Z","msg":"其實佢地識唔識咩係美債同稀土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8787ef5c2352ae6242776a9f5c673465ca97bcd9","tid":1420004,"uid":36134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"支那單方面捱打咋<br />\n神你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d855e032872b3a1fb21ea0333886dac8114a00f","tid":1420004,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"無一個中國人係無辜"},{"pid":"94c7347ad3d67c8d87868f6d5c1d6cf2a8740926","tid":1420004,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"有排你受呀大陸喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17af8bb5e883b7da9b86984dd23d595b16acc3e5","tid":1420004,"uid":299311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:25:38.000Z","msg":"係咪以為叫稀土就好稀有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00ba662b79bb44ce78f42b95fc97078b296add8","tid":1420004,"uid":139261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8787ef5c2352ae6242776a9f5c673465ca97bcd9","tid":1420004,"uid":36134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"支那單方面捱打咋<br />\n神你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:26:39.000Z","msg":"班傻閪成日以為美國輸嗰少少錢就係對佢哋嚟講係世界末日<br />\n自己輸十倍都未撚知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92de5bd72d4656d2f4fc271ee54c264fbe98432","tid":1420004,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17af8bb5e883b7da9b86984dd23d595b16acc3e5","tid":1420004,"uid":299311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c